::Battera::

She turned her head to see how well vulois was doing when, out in the 
distance, she caught the reflection of another bot in flight, heading 
for them. "Oh to the pit, now I've got two after my tail. That's it. 
I've had it. No more miss nice bat." She turned and headed for the 
canyon floor. She went into a nose dive and pulled up at the last 
second, coasting only a few feet off the canyon floor. She swung and 
glided in and out of the rock structures. She skimmed her wings along 
a small pond and the rose a few more feet.  She then made a sharp 
turn and quickly ducked into a cave.  She flew up into the ceiling of 
the cave and hung, upside down on a stalagtite.  She wrapped her 
wings around her and hid in the dark of the cave.
